{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "原初之力 第24章 1-1 罪孽沉眠之地",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "一行来到迦道夫和席菈的祖国勒福克斯。\\n不断涌出的黑暗魔力导致\\n那里已经化为一片沙漠。\\n若想前往龙之墓，就必须切断黑暗魔力。\\n于是一行决定寻找黑暗魔力的来源。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "这里就是勒福克斯？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_01_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "嗯……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_01_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "telop",
            "context": "\\n原初之力\\nDragalia Lost ～失落的龙约～ 第24章\\n \\n ",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "“起始之人”已经复活。\\n我们则对那自称泽诺斯的家伙\\n束手无策。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_01_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "为了寻求打败泽诺斯的方法，\\n我们前往亡国勒福克斯，\\n试图找到“龙之墓”让五龙觉醒。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_01_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "这里竟然曾经有一个国家，\\n真是令人难以置信啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_01_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "这里确实有过一个国家。\\n正是我所统治的勒福克斯……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_01_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "迦道夫，你没事吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_01_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "嗯。我一直都在思考，\\n终有一天我需要回到这里\\n面对自己的罪行。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_01_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "可在我犹豫之时，\\n时间却已经过去了这么久……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_01_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "眼前的这片光景，\\n正是我的罪过，亦是对我的惩罚。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_01_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "惩罚我这对战争和内乱束手无策，\\n什么都没能保护好的无能之人……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_01_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "话说，我能问你一个问题吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_01_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "勒福克斯是在战争中失败了对吧。\\n那现在这里难道不应该是\\n由战胜国来统治吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_01_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "即便这里的沙漠化是由龙所致，\\n可只要还有人在，\\n就一定会有抗争才对。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_01_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "可如今这里莫说是有国家，\\n连人们能不能在这里生存都是问题。\\n区区几十年就能让土地荒废成这样吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_01_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "你刚才说\\n对战争和内乱束手无策。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_01_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "如果战争是导致勒福克斯亡国的原因，\\n那导致这里变为沙漠的，\\n就是你所说的内乱吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_01_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "没错。\\n连战胜国都放弃了这片土地。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_01_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "至于为什么会放弃……\\n继续往前走你自然就能明白。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_01_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "（这前方究竟有着什么……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_01_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "停下……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_01_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "莱姬希？怎么了？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_01_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "检测到前方有黑暗魔力。\\n判断继续前进会有危险。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_01_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "你说有黑暗魔力？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_01_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "这黑暗魔力就是战胜国\\n放弃这片土地的原因。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_01_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "这前方原本有一大片湖水，\\n只不过现在已经干涸了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_01_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "龙之墓也在那里。\\n只是，从某个时间起，\\n那里就开始不断地涌出黑暗魔力。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_01_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "当时正值战争激烈之时，\\n我疲于应对战事。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_01_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "来源不明的黑暗魔力\\n扩散至全国范围，\\n将勒福克斯推向了恐惧的深渊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_01_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "敌国则趁着混乱入侵，\\n使得勒福克斯战败。\\n我和席菈便离开了这个国家……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_01_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "原来如此。\\n也就是说战胜国也拿这黑暗魔力没办法，\\n最后只能放弃这片土地。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_01_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "而沙漠化应该就是黑暗魔力\\n导致龙丧失理智的结果吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_01_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "总算理清了来龙去脉……\\n只是还有疑问没能解开。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_01_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "疑问。\\n这黑暗魔力的来源是哪里？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_01_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "如果勒福克斯尚在之时\\n就已经有了这黑暗魔力的话，\\n似乎不会是“起始之人”搞的鬼。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_01_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "来源……我也不清楚。\\n当时我将这一带的调查\\n都交给席菈负责监督了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_01_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "但我听说因为黑暗魔力和\\n狂暴化的魔兽的影响\\n使得调查进行得并不顺利。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_01_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "是吗。\\n那看来只能由我们自己来调查了。\\n你说是吧，尤蒂尔？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_01_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "嗯。只要找出来源，\\n也许就能得知\\n切断这黑暗魔力的方法。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_01_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "我明白了。\\n那我们就在这附近调查一下吧。\\n毕竟会有魔兽，大家都小心点。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_01_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "嗯。各位，我们出发！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_01_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "开始调查……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_01_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}